ECR Repository:

aws ecr create-repository
 --repository-name sample-webpage
aws ecr get-login-password --region <your-region> | docker login --username AWS --password-stdin <your-account-id>.dkr.ecr.<your-region>.amazonaws.com

Docker Image:

docker build -t sample-webpage .
docker tag sample-webpage:latest <your-account-id>.dkr.ecr.<your-region>.amazonaws.com/sample-webpage:latest
docker push <your-account-id>.dkr.ecr.<your-region>.amazonaws.com/sample-webpage:latest

ECS Cluster and Task Definition:

aws ecs create-cluster --cluster-name sample-cluster
aws ecs register-task-definition --cli-input-json file://task-definition.json

ECS Service:
aws ecs create-service --cli-input-json file://service-definition.json

Check the ECS service status:
aws ecs describe-services --cluster sample-cluster --services sample-service
